-- Aquascutum Gets Bids From YGM and Ittierre, Sunday Times Reports
-- B y   J e s s e   W e s t b r o o k
-- 2012-04-22T08:07:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-22/aquascutum-gets-bids-from-ygm-and-ittierre-sunday-times-reports.html
Aquascutum, a U.K. clothing
company, has attracted offers from  YGM Trading Ltd. (375)  and Ittierre
SpA, the Sunday Times reported, citing executives close to the
situation.  Aquascutum owner Harold Tillman put the 161-year-old
clothing label known for its trenchcoats into administration
this month.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jesse Westbrook in London at 
